sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant CLI as tet_cli
  participant API as Tet facade
  participant Runtime as tet_runtime
  participant Worker as SessionWorker
  participant Policy as Tet.Policy
  participant Tools as Tool Executor
  participant Store as Tet.Store adapter
  participant Bus as Tet.EventBus

  User->>CLI: tet edit S "make change"
  CLI->>API: Tet.send_prompt(S, prompt, mode: :execute)
  API->>Runtime: dispatch %Tet.Command.UserPrompt{}
  Runtime->>Store: append user message + event
  Runtime->>Worker: run turn
  Worker->>Policy: check tool intent
  alt read tool allowed
    Policy-->>Worker: allow
    Worker->>Tools: run read tool
    Tools->>Store: save tool_run
    Tools-->>Worker: result
  else patch proposed
    Policy-->>Worker: require approval
    Worker->>Store: save diff artifact + pending approval
    Worker->>Bus: publish approval.created
  else blocked
    Policy-->>Worker: block reason
    Worker->>Store: save blocked tool_run
    Worker->>Bus: publish tool.blocked
  end
  Bus-->>CLI: stream %Tet.Event{}
  CLI-->>User: render timeline/diff/approval id
